double and triple shifts.

01:13.953 --> 01:16.021
Personnel need rest or people die.

01:16.055 --> 01:18.690
Sounds like you should be doing my job.

01:18.725 --> 01:20.759
Jumper off a six-story building.

01:20.793 --> 01:24.217
Landed on a parked minivan.
160 over 90, 158.

01:24.251 --> 01:26.331
