I have a strict policy
of calm efficiency.

05:42.410 --> 05:46.046
No hysterics, no yelling.
Just simple patient care.

05:46.081 --> 05:49.984
Nothing makes me happier than
the words "calm efficiency."

05:50.018 --> 05:51.352
Good.

05:51.386 --> 05:53.020
Then you and I are gonna
make a great team.

05:53.054 --> 05:55.022
