His chart says A-positive from
the dog tags we found on him.

13:20.408 --> 13:22.510
Then his dog tags
are barking the wrong tune.

13:22.544 --> 13:24.979
Type and cross says B-Positive.

13:25.013 --> 13:28.549
Hey, hey, that... that is not Alex Demos.

13:28.583 --> 13:30.317
