to seem that way.

13:30.352 --> 13:31.418
Yeah, called my friends at the VA,

13:31.453 --> 13:33.821
and Alex Demos is a woman.

13:33.855 --> 13:35.489
That's not a woman.

13:35.524 --> 13:38.225
Oh, guess that explains why
this guy isn't A-Positive.

13:38.260 --> 13:40.027
Yeah.

13:40.061 --> 13:41.996
So then what the hell
is he doing with her dog tags?

13:42.030 --> 13:44.999
<i>[PERCUSSIVE MUSIC]</i>

13:45.033 --> 13:51.839
<i>♪ </i>

13:51.873 --> 13:53.841
- Karen Brantley.
- Max.

13:53.875 --> 13:55.175
Thanks for meeting me.

13:55.210 --> 13:57.511
